[According to the Global Polio Eradication Initiative update that reported the initial positive ESs in Uganda, the virus was identified as associated with the outbreak ongoing in Chad. These more recent reports link the virus with that circulating in the Sudan but further investigation reveals the outbreak in Sudan was linked to that in Chad -- a good demonstration of the high mobility of the population and the impact on virus circulation/transmission.

A map of Uganda can be found at https://www.worldatlas.com/maps/uganda. - Mod.MPP

